title: 이달의소녀탐구 #505 (LOONA TV #505)
members: Yves, Choerry, HyunJin, HaSeul, YeoJin, Go Won
summary:
0:01 -- Yves, Choerry, and HyunJin: "Aeong~ 😸" (a cut to Freddie Mercury saying 'Aeong')
0:03 -- Choerry is scared that she will become a cat one day. Yves thinks about when they finally get their first win (when? ;-;), what they will say. HyunJin: "Aeong~"
0:17 -- They are on a field trip according to Go Won and she asks where they are. - YeoJin: "We are in LOOΠΔTHEWORLD. Only LOOΠΔ members get to be here." HaSeul and Go Won do not agree and YeoJin gives in by saying that all the others are related to LOOΠΔ.

0:38 -- HaSeul has never been to a field trip and the two tease her for being too old.
